entries.arrived_at_delivery: Roger that, pilot. Arrival at delivery location acknowledged. Await the drop-off vessel here.
entries.attack_notify: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <pcontrast3  Warning. Enemy craft inbound.pcontrast1 >
entries.attack_stopped: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <pcontrast3  Enemy threat neutralized.pcontrast1 >
entries.docking_complete_delivery: And... you're clear. Say, I don't recognize your ship markings. Eh, whatever... my job is done.
entries.failed_destroyed: The mission is a wash, pilot. The delivery ship was destroyed. Return to base for debriefing.
entries.found_loc_d: Transmitting coordinates of delivery location. Proceed to the waypoint and meet the drop-off vessel.
entries.hello_d: Are you the agent I'm looking for? I'm ready to transfer the package. Do you copy?
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the drop-off vessel by pressing the 'U' key, and he will transfer the leaked information to your ship. Once you have it, return to the station for debriefing and anaysis.
entries.quest_location_d: The drop-off is supposed to happen elsewhere in the Corellia system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the coordinates provided by CorSec Command. The drop-off vessel will meet you there.
entries.split_quest_alert: Mission successful. Return to CorSec Station.
entries.title: Corellia System: Intercept the Leaked Information
entries.title_d: CorSec Command wants you to take the place of the Cloak agent and intercept the leaked information that is being delivered. You should travel to the coordinates provided by Command, dock with the delivery ship, and receive the information he is carrying. Once you have it, return to the station for analysis.
